Hey, hey, I've never seen you before, so don't
wander around naked!

Um? You haven't registered with the guild yet...
Are you a magical girl, I wonder?

If you join, you'll be able to use the facilities
here, so it would be great if you could meet the
guild's guildmaster, Gilcho, and register.

Welcome back~... Oh, you're a first-time visitor,
aren't you? How can you be comfortable dressed
like that?

Welcome back~... Oh, you're a first-time visitor,
aren't you? Could you be the magical girl from the
other day?

Forget about that... I just talked to Gilcho a
little while ago.
Yes, Gilcho told me to ask you about this place.

So, you've joined the guild! Thank you very much.
I'm just a regular house manager in charge of this
place, nice to meet you.

You can think of this guild house as your magical
girls' base. For now, let me give you a brief
explanation.

Okay! I know it might be tough, but let's do our
best from now on~
Welcome back~! Take care not to catch a cold...
Welcome back~! What's going on today?
